---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="astro-cube">
  <style>
    .erotic-button {
      align-items: center;
      background-image: linear-gradient(144deg, #9843d4, #5643d3 50%, #246ad3);
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: rgba(151, 65, 252, 0.2) 0 15px 30px -5px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      display: flex;
      font-family: Phantomsans, sans-serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      justify-content: center;
      line-height: 1em;
      max-width: 100%;
      min-width: 140px;
      padding: 3px;
      text-decoration: none;
      user-select: none;
      -webkit-user-select: none;
      touch-action: manipulation;
      white-space: nowrap;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .erotic-button:active,
    .erotic-button:hover {
      outline: 0;
    }

    .erotic-button span {
      background-color: rgb(5, 6, 45);
      padding: 16px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      transition: 300ms;
    }

    .erotic-button:hover span {
      background: none;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .erotic-button {
        font-size: 24px;
        min-width: 196px;
      }
    }

    /* Estilos para el diseño responsivo */
    .flex-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .content, .image {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      max-width: 500px; /* Ajusta el tamaño máximo de la imagen */
    }

    .centered-image {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .centered-image img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      max-width: 800px; /* Ajusta el tamaño máximo de la imagen */
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .flex-container {
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .content {
        flex: 1;
        margin-right: 20px;
      }

      .image {
        flex: 0 0 auto;
      }

      .centered-image img {
        max-width: 700px; /* Ajusta el tamaño máximo de la imagen para pantallas grandes */
      }
    }
  </style>

  <main>
    <article class="region prose wrapper hero flex-container">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="title-container">
          <h1>Horny Club</h1>
          <button class="erotic-button" role="button">
            <span>Access to the club</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <h2>
          The best <a>erotic private club</a> in all the internet
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="image">
        <img src="images/women4.png" alt="Descriptive Alt Text" />
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="region prose wrapper">
      <ul role="list" class="grid features">
        <li class="flow">
          <h3>How can I access?</h3>
          <p>
            At the moment the access to the club is <em>limited</em> and just available, with a <em>personal invitation.</em>
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="flow">
          <h3>What can I find in the club?</h3>
          <p>
            In our club you will enjoy different types of <em>shows</em> and
            <em>special rooms</em> streaming from our models.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="flow">
          <h3>Is it safe?</h3>
          <p>
            Yes, our club is 100% client anonymous with <a href="">a 0 logs policy</a> so every client can preserve their privacy, just identified with an 
            <em>individual code</em> that gives access to the rooms.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="flow">
          <h3>How can I be a HornyClub Model?</h3>
          <p>
            To be a model you have to go <a href="/model">to the registration page</a>, there you will have all the conditions to start streaming and start earning a minimum of <em>1k every month</em>. Limited places for models.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <div class="centered-image">
      <img src="images/women5.png" alt="Sexy trio of girls" />
    </div>

    <footer class="region prose wrapper">
      <a href="">© HornyClub 2024. All rights reserved.</a>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>
